<div class="content-fragment-inner macmillan-content-fragment-inner"><div class="content-fragment-top macmillan-content-fragment-top"></div><div class="content-fragment-content">







	



    <div class="abbreviated-post-header"></div>
<div class="abbreviated-post">
    <h4 class="post-name">Please help I need advice I feel helpless</h4>
</div>
<div class="abbreviated-post-header"></div>
<div class="content-list-header"></div>
<ul class="content-list">
        <li class="content-item post-starter">
        




<div class="full-post-header  post-starter "></div>
<div class="full-post-container fiji-full-post-container evolution2-full-post-container"  data-reply-id="100606"  data-thread-starter="true" >
<div class="full-post  post-starter ">
	<a name="100606"></a>
	<a name="100606"></a>
	<div class="post-author">
		<table class="post-author-details-table fiji-post-author-details-table evolution2-post-author-details-table" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
			<tr>
				<td class="post-author-avatar-cell fiji-post-author-avatar-cell evolution2-post-author-avatar-cell">
					<span class="avatar">
													<a href="/members/cheesie">
								<img src="/cfs-filesystemfile/__key/communityserver-components-imagefileviewer/communityserver-components-selectableavatars-64e6583d-e9be-44d9-a227-06c829b8c238/avatar.png_2D00_32x32.png" border="0" alt="Cheesie" />
							</a>
											</span>
				</td>
				<td class="post-author-user-cell fiji-post-author-user-cell evolution2-post-author-user-cell">
				   <div class="user-name-post-date fiji-user-name-post-date evolution2-user-name-post-date">
						Posted by <span class="user-name">
															<a class="internal-link view-user-profile" href="/members/cheesie">
									<span></span>Cheesie
								</a>
													</span>
						<div class="post-date">
							<span class="label">
																	on
															</span>
							<span class="value"><a href='/cancer_types/breast-cancer/f/38/t/100606' class="internal-link view-post">29 Oct 2015 11:29 PM</a></span>
						</div>
																	</div>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</div>
	
	
	<div class="post-content user-defined-markup">
					<p><span style="font-family:Helvetica, Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:16px;">My sisters law has just been diagnosed with breast cancer with it also in lymph nodes under arm ,she is due to have op on Friday week , we are all in shock she has been told she will have all the treatment offered over the next ten years , but what I need to ask those of you who have been through this awful thing is how can I help what will she need please can you enlighten me to the perhaps simple things that the leaflets don&#39;t say yet you found helped your comfort or aided your recovery ,thanks for listening</span></p><div style="clear:both;"></div>
					</div>

	



	  

<div class="fiji-post-details-container-outer evolution2-post-details-container-outer">
	<table class="post-details-container fiji-post-details-container evolution2-post-details-container" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
		<tr>
															<td class="post-actions-cell fiji-post-actions-cell evolution2-post-actions-cell">
				<div class="post-actions">
