	<div class="post-content user-defined-markup">
					<p>Hi Cheesie, well done for wanting to support your sister in law and you ve already got lots of wise advice on here. There are great leaflets that MacMillan produce giving advice about how to support loved ones with cancer and how to talk with them. I d definitely recommend downloading them (available on the main Macmillan site) and maybe order your own paper copies for future reference.</p><div style="clear:both;"></div>
