	<div class="post-content user-defined-markup">
					<p>Dear Grogg,</p>
<p>I recently moved home and am also having quite a bit of work done so there are always builders&#39; vans in our parking area.&nbsp; I must say I just tell everyone why I&#39;m not at work (though returning in a couple of weeks) and there are a number of advantages.&nbsp; One of them is that people tend to help out more (I have dodgy hip, aggravated by Letrozole and live alone)..ie help me carry stuff.&nbsp; But apart from that, I am generally an open person and find it easier to actively tell folks, albeit briefly, what&#39;s going on with me.&nbsp; Having said that, I never post anything on FB about my condition.&nbsp; Just use it for exchanging jokes etc..</p>
<p></p>
<p>Pepys xx</p><div style="clear:both;"></div>
					</div>

	



	  
