	<div class="post-content user-defined-markup">
					<p>Hi Grogg,</p>
<p>Your reference to lack of sleep made me smile! :-) send her a text late at night letting her know that you are not sleeping well :-)</p>
<p>My advice regarding the neighbour is to say matter of fact &#39; I&#39;ve had breast cancer recently and getting over it&quot; if you convey the information in a normal tone, she may be less likely to freak out, I think. But if she does freak out then that is her and not your doing :-) Judith xx</p><div style="clear:both;"></div>
					</div>

	



	  
