	<div class="post-content user-defined-markup">
					<p>Thanks again for sharing i feel iv gained alot already from you all&nbsp;</p>
<p>i will definitely not text and as same questions , was hoping to me more newsy about life this end and encourage talk of her daughter</p>
<p>i will look up other groups too although im not finding it easy to navegate this site yet but will keep trying</p>
<p>i have taken photos of the seat belt idea and the nail stuff i didnt even know your nails could be affected :(</p>
<p>i will now sit tight now &nbsp;i havnt told her about my need for advice ,</p>
<p>ill see how it all affects her and wait to see how we can help i will ask about the news spreader idea though,</p>
<p>she made a family whats app group called it &quot;the dirty little c word&quot; so when she has news she tells us altogether which has been helpful , i want to tell her about your site but dont want to intrude on how shes dealing with it because of distance i cant see her face and txt its not easy to read into at times is it ,</p>
<p>grogg sorry to hear about your sleep or lack of it, do you feel more worn out because of it or do you catch up during the day</p>
<p>thanks again all&nbsp;</p>
<p></p><div style="clear:both;"></div>
					</div>

	



	  

